  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/0e55b594d1cfb5228c434840b4b17c3b.poster.avif?t=1743586642\" width=640 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/0e55b594d1cfb5228c434840b4b17c3b.webm?t=1743586642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/0e55b594d1cfb5228c434840b4b17c3b.mp4?t=1743586642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In this single player game you will be using an in-game computer to message friends with Yak to stay connected and help each other survive the zombie world, Explore the web to see what's going on in the world and clear emails as the game progresses.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/0b366daabbbe02a8cac4e96230f69d42.poster.avif?t=1743586642\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/0b366daabbbe02a8cac4e96230f69d42.webm?t=1743586642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/0b366daabbbe02a8cac4e96230f69d42.mp4?t=1743586642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Leave your computer at any time and explore the non-digital world!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/ef3ab889af046670e621aca51c2603c9.poster.avif?t=1743586642\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/ef3ab889af046670e621aca51c2603c9.webm?t=1743586642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/ef3ab889af046670e621aca51c2603c9.mp4?t=1743586642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore your 'empty' apartment building for items to assist your nearby friends and uncover lost last messages from old tenants.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/40341d4b6665f2e67be89362a070fdc1.poster.avif?t=1743586642\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/40341d4b6665f2e67be89362a070fdc1.webm?t=1743586642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1141030/extras/40341d4b6665f2e67be89362a070fdc1.mp4?t=1743586642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Watch your back! This world is still full of unfriendly people ~ including the vicious infected!",
